name: daisy
description:
i wrote this song for my girlfriend to help her cope with her grandfather's death.

never really understood the track until my own grandfather passed recently.

if you're going through grief, i hope this helps you find solace.

------

daisy is the 6th track off Maha Jeffery's upcoming album C.A.I.S.O.

this is an early copy of the single.
 
daisy will be available on all digital streaming platforms on 24th nov 2021.

written and performed by Maha Jeffery
lead guitar by Raz Karan
produced by Sid Murshid
art by Amio Mon
